{"tid":531694,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[肥婆]矮仔入黎，搵到增高方法","createTime":"2018-01-17T05:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T00:30:07.000Z","uid":22927,"like":26,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91c36a1a499c43c20050a1710cf32a8dc360d57f","tid":531694,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"上次搭飛機坐CX，<br />\n有條肥婆，大約半噸重啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n一開閘就應聲彈出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n慌死執輸咁一嘢得撚左落個位到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n一坐底就抽起左右個扶手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n唔洗講啦，一邊籮柚佔一個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n霸左左邊一半同右邊一半，<br />\n係四十秒之後已經發出震耳欲聾嘅鼻塞聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n之後有個後生仔上機，大約170左右啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就坐係佢隔籬，<br />\n由日本返香港四粒鐘，<br />\n全程比條肥婆夾撚住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n企起身嗰陣見返個後生仔，<br />\n屌！成2米高，初初都以為自己眼花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n之後見到佢落機出機門嗰下撞到個門框我就confirm 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n原來個後生仔真係比個肥婆夾撚到瘦左高左，<br />\n如果大家想增高唔撚洗再食咩增高丸啦，<br />\n搭hkexpress 坐肥婆隔籬，<br />\n坐位更窄效果更佳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n160都變230!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屌你老母死肥婆，搭飛機就買兩個位啦！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1f117bd2ffa3225e2db8a3c3e14d06fab04bd5cb","tid":531694,"uid":51978,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得自己好幽默？"},{"pid":"0ba51edd048f8513cf9baf5ceb115bb0f